          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-higgsfield-ai"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of AI video tools over the past year. Most of them? Forgettable. They churn out stiff, robotic clips that look like they came from a slideshow generator. Then I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Higgsfield AI",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and the difference was immediate — smooth camera pans, dramatic dolly shots, and footage that actually *feels* like cinema.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tutorial walks you through everything you need to go from zero to your first polished AI-generated video. No prior video editing experience required. Just follow each step.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Higgsfield AI?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://goto.higgsfield.ai/c/6249333/2949196/34954"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Higgsfield AI",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is a video generation platform built around one specific strength: cinematic realism. While other AI tools focus on generating static images or short looping clips, Higgsfield puts serious effort into replicating real-world camera movements — tracking shots, crane lifts, handheld shakes, drone flyovers, and rack focus transitions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform runs in your browser. You sign up, type a prompt describing your scene, choose a camera style, and hit generate. That's it. Under the hood, Higgsfield's models have been trained on film footage to understand how directors and cinematographers actually move cameras. The output reflects that training.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've used it for product promo clips, social media reels, and even concept visuals for a short film pitch. Every time, the results surprised me with how natural the motion looked.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Create Your Account",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://higgsfield.ai"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "higgsfield.ai",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and sign up. The process takes about sixty seconds. You can register with an email address or use Google sign-in for faster access.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/higgsfield-ai-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you're in, you'll land on the main dashboard. From here, you have two primary options: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generate",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " (create new videos) and ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Library",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " (browse your past creations and community submissions). Spend a minute exploring the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "community library",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — it's a goldmine for inspiration. You'll see what other creators are building and get a feel for prompt styles that work well.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
