        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Click ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generate",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " to open the creation interface. Here's where the magic starts.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your prompt describes the scene you want. Be specific. Vague prompts produce generic results. Detailed prompts produce cinematic results.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Weak prompt:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " \"A car driving.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Strong prompt:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " \"A matte-black sports car speeding along a coastal highway at golden hour, ocean waves crashing on rocks below, shot from a low-angle tracking camera following the vehicle.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/higgsfield-ai-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Notice the difference? The strong prompt tells Higgsfield what to film *and* how to film it. That second part — the camera instruction — is where this tool genuinely outperforms its competitors. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Learn more prompt strategies here",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
