        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rack focus",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Shifting focus between foreground and background",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pick one that matches your scene's energy. A drone shot works beautifully for landscapes and real estate. A handheld style adds grit to urban or action scenes. Dolly-in creates tension for product reveals or character close-ups.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can also combine camera movements in longer generations, letting the platform transition between styles within a single clip. This produces results that feel like actual film sequences rather than AI-generated loops.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
