          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If something feels off, tweak your prompt and regenerate. Small changes — swapping \"golden hour\" for \"overcast daylight,\" or \"tracking shot\" for \"slow dolly\" — can dramatically shift the output.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
